data.Name: Shawn Mendes: Wonder, The World Tour
data.Description: For the health and safety of everyone attending Shawn Mendes, Wonder: The World Tour, all tour dates will abide by local laws, guidance from public health authorities, and venue COVID-19 policies. Enhanced health and safety policies may be put in place at any time for tour dates at the discretion of the venue or tour. For the most current COVID-19 information relating to the tour date you plan to attend, please visit the venue website.
